(Staeger, 1842)
</emphasis>
(Dolichopodinae)
</taxonomicName>
— 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[916,1106,657,683]" pageId="36" pageNumber="37">
new to 
<collectingCountry box="[1002,1106,657,683]" name="Portugal" pageId="36" pageNumber="37">Portugal</collectingCountry>
</emphasis>
</paragraph>
